
## Dependencies

The plugin automatically installs these dependencies:
- `python-core`
- `python-twisted-web`
- `python-json`
- `gstreamer1.0` and plugins (base, good, bad, ugly)
- `ffmpeg`

## Usage

### Plugin Controls

- **OK**: Play selected channel
- **Menu**: Open settings
- **Green**: Reset audio
- **Left/Right**: Switch categories
- **CH+/CH-**: Adjust audio delay
- **Up/Down**: Navigate channels

### Web Interface

Access at `http://your-box-ip:8080/ipstreamer`

- Create/delete categories
- Add/edit/remove channels
- Drag channels to reorder
- Real-time sync with plugin

## Configuration Files

- **Plugin**: `/usr/lib/enigma2/python/Plugins/Extensions/IPStreamer/`
- **Playlists**: `/etc/enigma2/ipstreamer/ipstreamer_*.json`
- **Settings**: Stored in Enigma2 settings

## Changelog

### v8.0 (Latest)
- Multi-category playlist support
- New color themes (Orange, Teal, Lime)
- Web interface with drag-and-drop
- Audio/video delay control (0.5s increments)
- Network status monitoring
- GitHub auto-updates
- Improved picon support

